{"tid":2074551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美兩航母菲律賓海軍演示威","createTime":"2020-06-22T07:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T07:42:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1b0b8f4719563a258c54aa5a91c32d08dcaa03","tid":2074551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200622/B4MWN6GMTYV5H7M554VOPQEDJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200622%2FB4MWN6GMTYV5H7M554VOPQEDJ4%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=664fe018\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200622%2FB4MWN6GMTYV5H7M554VOPQEDJ4%2F&h=282ae449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200622/B4MWN6GMTYV5H7M554VOPQEDJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美兩航母菲律賓海軍演示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JJO77XBZ7MJEQOYQ4QVSMAVDFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJJO77XBZ7MJEQOYQ4QVSMAVDFA.jpg&h=337d4c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍頻頻以軍機擾台之際，美國航母「羅斯福號」（圖）及「尼米茲號」昨在菲律賓海，展開雙航母軍演。有分析認為，美軍是要向中國傳達訊息，就是即使新型冠狀病毒疫情大流行，美軍將繼續在區內維持強大力量，震懾中國。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸軍機頻出動 兩周七闖台空域  學者：北京進行「壓力測試」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析：維持區內阻嚇力<br />\n<br />\n據美國太平洋艦隊司令部發佈訊息，羅斯福號和尼米茲號。。。。。局勢趨緊、新型冠狀病毒肆虐之際，提升自身作戰技巧和戰備。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國智庫「外交關係協會」雙月刊「外交事務」（。。。。。意願或能力，容易擦槍走火，甚至作出中期封鎖或攻台的決定。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，美方嚇阻力量較昔日減弱，或將導致美。。。。。要降低戰爭風險，需要重建美國阻嚇能力的可信度。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"}]}